 dog parks provide a safe haven for the city’s 100,000+ residents and their canine companions.\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/cities/el-paso\",\"image\":\"/images/cities/el-paso-tx/hero.webp\",\"datePublished\":\"2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-02-06T02:41:18.951Z\",\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Indoor Dog Park\",\"logo\":{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/images/logo/logo-512.png\"}},\"about\":{\"@type\":\"City\",\"name\":\"El Paso, TX\"},\"mainEntity\":{\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/cities/el-paso#itemlist\"},\"containsPlace\":[{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/a-better-canine-4-u\",\"name\":\"A Better Canine 4 U\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/a-better-canine-4-u\",\"sameAs\":[\"http://www.abettercanine4u.com/\"],\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"streetAddress\":\"8809 Norton St\",\"addressLocality\":\"El Paso\",\"addressRegion\":\"TX\",\"postalCode\":\"79904\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"},\"telephone\":\"(915) 751-7200\",\"aggregateRating\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateRating\",\"ratingValue\":4.6,\"reviewCount\":9},\"geo\":{\"@type\":\"GeoCoordinates\",\"latitude\":31.8630502,\"longitude\":-106.4360506}},{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/agave-pet-grooming\",\"name\":\"Agave Pet Grooming\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/agave-pet-grooming\",\"sameAs\":[\"http://groomer.io/schedule/agave\"],\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"streetAddress\":\"10420 Montwood Dr ste F\",\"addressLocality\":\"El Paso\",\"addressRegion\":\"TX\",\"postalCode\":\"79935\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"},\"telephone\":\"(915) 270-9474\",\"aggregateRating\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateRating\",\"ratingValue\":4.7,\"reviewCount\":118},\"geo\":{\"@type\":\"GeoCoordinates\",\"latitude\":31.7712671,\"longitude\":-106.3387576}},{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":